## Git
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

## Build output — CRITICAL: obj/ contains project.assets.json files baked on Windows
## with 'C:\Program Files (x86)\...\NuGetPackages' fallback paths.
## If these are copied into the container the publish step fails even after restore.
**/obj/
**/bin/

## IDE / editor
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo

## Docker files themselves
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml

## CI/CD
.github/
.gitlab-ci.yml

## Docs / misc
README.md
QUICK_START.md
AI_HANDOFF_PROMPT.md
*.md

## Local secrets — never bake into image
**/secrets.json
**/appsettings.Development.json

## Logs
logs/
*.log
